Function: adds a new menu item to the Settings menu (Account Administration)

Required plugin: none

instructions:

1: copy the "hmail_settings" folder to your plugin directory.
   <install directory>\plugins\settings

2: copy <install directory>\plugins\settings\config\config.inc.php.dist 
   to   <install directory>\plugins\settings\config\config.inc.php
 
3: add "settings" to your plugin array settings in your <install directory>\config\main.inc.php
   $rcmail_config['plugins'] = array('settings')
   
   If configured correctly, your Settings options should have a new menu item, Account Administration.